  40:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_exti.c ****         interrupts pending registers which allow to distinguish which transition
  41:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_exti.c ****         occurs:
